bullets: Sign in WW Vip access package Master the Stock Market 6 month mentorship Trading Whales on Wall Street Mentorship Program The Whales on Wall Street Mentorship is designed for anyone who wants to take control of their financial future by mastering the art of day trading stock options. Whether you’re a complete beginner or someone with a little trading experience, this program will walk you step-by-step through everything you need to know about trading options with confidence. What You Will Learn Understanding Options Contracts We start with the foundations. You’ll learn what an option contract is, how it works, and why traders use them. I’ll break down calls, puts, strike prices, expiration dates, premiums, and the Greeks in simple terms, so you’ll understand exactly how options move and gain value. By the end of this stage, you’ll know how to read an options chain and recognize what contracts best fit your goals.

Market Structure & Setups Before jumping into trades, you need to know how the market moves. I’ll teach you how to read price action, spot supply and demand zones, and identify break-and-retest levels. These setups will help you see where big money is moving so you can enter with precision instead of guessing.

Buying and Selling Options Once you understand contracts and market structure, we’ll move into execution. You’ll learn how to buy and sell options step-by-step, from picking the right strike price to managing contracts as they move. I’ll show you both sides of the trade—going long on calls and puts, as well as how to sell contracts
